description: The fund invests at least 80% of its total assets in the securities of the underlying index and in American Depositary Receipts ("ADRs") and Global Depositary Receipts ("GDRs") based on the securities in the underlying index. The objective of the underlying index is to provide exposure to exchange-listed companies globally that provide educational products and services. The fund generally will use a replication strategy. It is non-diversified.
name: Global X Education ETF
